{"seriesId":184545,"title":"刻刻","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/37798039/37798039.18500082","descriptionFirst":"佑河樹里は、家族との同居に疲れを感じていた。そんな日常は一本の電話によって切り裂かれる。誘拐された兄と甥。助けるための時間は、父と樹里との諍いにより、刻一刻と過ぎ去っていく。祖父はそんな二人を恫喝すると、ある術を披露した…\n\n佑河樹里:安済知佳／間島翔子:瀬戸麻沙美／じいさん:山路和弘／佑河真:岩田龍門／佑河貴文:辻谷耕史／佑河翼:野島裕史／佐河順治:郷田ほづみ／潮見:内田夕夜／迫:吉野裕行\n\n原作:堀尾 省太「刻刻」（講談社『モーニング・ツー』所載）／監督:大橋誉志光／音楽:未知瑠／シリーズ構成:木村 暢／アニメーションキャラクターデザイン総作画監督:日向 正樹／キャラクター原案:梅津 泰臣\n\n© 堀尾省太・講談社／「刻刻」製作委員会\n\n次話→so37798050","tags":["SF/ファンタジー","ホラー/サスペンス/推理","モーニング","2018年冬アニメ","ジェノスタジオ"],"cours":"2018-冬","colKey":"か","relatedSeries":[],"episodes":[{"contentId":"so37798039","episodeNo":1,"title":"刻刻　㐧壱刻","viewCounter":3270,"commentCounter":171,"mylistCounter":66,"lengthSeconds":1440,"startTime":"2026-03-01T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/37798039/37798039.18500082"},{"contentId":"so37798050","episodeNo":2,"title":"刻刻　㐧弐刻","viewCounter":1111,"commentCounter":86,"mylistCounter":1,"lengthSeconds":1440,"startTime":"2026-03-01T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/37798050/37798050.82186826"},{"contentId":"so37798049","episodeNo":3,"title":"刻刻　㐧参刻","viewCounter":955,"commentCounter":77,"mylistCounter":0,"lengthSeconds":1440,"startTime":"2026-03-01T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/37798049/37798049.41008483"},{"contentId":"so37798048","episodeNo":4,"title":"刻刻　㐧肆刻","viewCounter":884,"commentCounter":65,"mylistCounter":0,"lengthSeconds":1440,"startTime":"2026-03-01T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/37798048/37798048.85308949"},{"contentId":"so37798047","episodeNo":5,"title":"刻刻　㐧伍刻","viewCounter":800,"commentCounter":64,"mylistCounter":0,"lengthSeconds":1440,"startTime":"2026-03-01T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/37798047/37798047.9412854"},{"contentId":"so37798045","episodeNo":6,"title":"刻刻　㐧陸刻","viewCounter":807,"commentCou